							<h1 class="entry-title">Updates and Resources</h1>

						<p class="post-meta"> by <span class="author vcard"><a href="https://vsnb.org/author/sherry-vsnb/" title="Posts by Sherry VSNB" rel="author">Sherry VSNB</a></span> | <a href="https://vsnb.org/category/community-events/" rel="category tag">Community Events</a>, <a href="https://vsnb.org/category/featured/" rel="category tag">Featured</a>, <a href="https://vsnb.org/category/school-events/" rel="category tag">School Events</a></p>
