					<h4 class="p1"><strong>This page contains the most up-to-date school-wide communications and information from the Village School regarding COVID-19. Classroom teachers are corresponding directly with their students regarding distance learning.</strong></h4>
<h4 class="p1"></h4>
<h4 class="p1"><strong>ANNOUNCEMENTS SENT TO FAMILIES: </strong></h4>
<p class="p1"><strong><span class="s1">•<a href="../covid-19-letter-to-families-4-27-20-2/">April 27 – </a></span></strong><a href="../covid-19-letter-to-families-4-27-20-2/"><span class="s1"><b>Distance Learning Resources, Information, and Online Safety; Plus, Join Mr. Newbold for Informal Google Meetings about Supporting Your Students</b></span></a></p>
<p class="p1"><strong><span class="s1">•<a href="../covid-19-letter-to-families-4-9-20/">April 9 – Spring Break Information &amp; Resources; Plus, Yearbook Details &amp; Faculty/Staff Feedback Form</a></span></strong></p>
<p class="p1"><strong><span class="s1">•<a href="../covid-19-letter-to-families-3-26-20/">March 26 VSNB Dismissed Through End of School Year</a></span></strong></p>
<p class="p1"><strong><span class="s1">•<a href="../covid-19-letter-to-families-3-25-20/">March 25 “</a><a href="../covid-19-letter-to-families-3-25-20/">Stay Home/Stay Safe” COVID-19 update</a> </span></strong></p>
<p class="p1"><strong><span class="s1">•<a href="../covid-19-letter-to-families-3-23-20/">March 23 COVID-19 update </a></span></strong></p>
<p class="p1"><strong><span class="s1">•<a href="../covid-19-letter-to-families-3-20-20/">March 20 communication to families</a> regarding Student Work, Free Meals, EPIC Update, Art Projects, and Preparing for the Long Haul </span></strong></p>
<p><strong><span class="s1">•<a href="../covid-19-letter-to-families-3-16-20/">School Closure Information</a> regarding communicating with the school; picking up and dropping off student assignments; and special note for healthcare workers and other Vermonters essential to the COVID-19 response. </span></strong></p>
<p><strong><span class="s1">•<a href="../covid-19-letter-to-families-3-15-20/">Village School to CLOSE on Tuesday, March 17, for Three Weeks</a></span></strong></p>
<p class="p1"><strong><span class="s1"><a href="../?page_id=5559&amp;preview=true">•March 13 letter from the Village School with COVID-19 updates and new procedures taking effect. </a></span></strong></p>
<p class="p1"><strong><span class="s1"><a href="../covid-19-3-9/">•March 9, 2020</a> letter from the Village School regarding COVID-19. </span></strong></p>
<h4></h4>
<h4><strong>COVID-19 RECOMMENDED RESOURCES:</strong></h4>
